reviewText: All arrived in good shape and all played with good viewing quality.

I got two Bambi's and a movie that wasn't on the list I was supposed to get. I was still happy with the collections. All the movies were in good condition and played perfectly. I would recommend purchasing from this buyer.
If you like Disney & your kids enjoy their shows, this collection has some great shows in this collection.

Perfect bulk buy for the classic disney lover. Great price and every single movie played perfect with no problems. All come in original case which are all in great shape.

Price was great! Arrived quickly and my kids started watching it! Unfortunately, it was missing a movie. When I notified them about the issue they told me there was nothing they could do. Kind of sucked since we were missing the movie Mulan and my daughters love that movie.
The price was fantastic and fair. I have an Autistic child that is obessed with VHS tapes (Disney). I am so grateful for access to these collections.
